": 26376, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313348}, {"id": 25097, "content": "-有事吗\n-没 没有\n实际上有一肚子话想说?", "image": null, "praise_count": 97, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 282109}, {"id": 25098, "content": "干嘛呢或者干什么呢   如果不熟只要一听到这几个字马上来气，我干什么关你丫屁事啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 255053}, {"id": 25354, "content": "嗨", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1156718}, {"id": 25610, "content": "多喝热水", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 284207}, {"id": 25355, "content": "嗯", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 292004}, {"id": 25100, "content": "在干嘛呢？ 没干嘛.....", "image": null, "praise_count": 362, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 265691}, {"id": 25612, "content": "→_→", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 279345}, {"id": 26124, "content": "那你多喝热水?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 311240}, {"id": 25101, "content": "你要这么想我也没办法。", "image": null, "praise_count": 925, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305722}, {"id": 25102, "content": "我考砸了，你肯定考的比我好?", "image": null, "praise_count": 413, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 162698}, {"id": 26382, "content": "生气啦？\n没有。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313388}, {"id": 30734, "content": "男：别别别,你先听我说完先 女：那你说啊 男：xxxxxxx 女：我不听 我不听 我不听...", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 335706}, {"id": 25103, "content": "嗯。好的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305725}, {"id": 25359, "content": "你干嘛呢\n坐着", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 306442}, {"id": 25104, "content": "出来见见？", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 145609}, {"id": 25360, "content": "随便", "image": "img/option/opti